OL,3,CConservative rep blames postal vote
OL,4,Cdelays on councils 'ineptitude'
OL,6,FA representative for Conservatives
OL,7,FAbroad has hit out at "the
OL,8,Fadministrative ineptitude of electoral
OL,9,Freturning officers" for delays in
OL,10,Foverseas voters receiving their postal
OL,11,Fballots.
OL,13,FRobert McDowall is the regional
OL,14,Fcoordinator for the Channel Islands
OL,15,Fwhere just under a third of the
OL,16,Fpopulation is now eligible to take
OL,17,Fpart in the UK General Election
OL,18,Ffollowing changes to British law.
