OL,3,CConservative rep blames postal vote
OL,4,Cdelays on councils 'ineptitude'
OL,6,FA 15-year time limit on British
OL,7,FCitizens abroad being able to vote in
OL,8,Ftheir former constituency has now been
OL,9,Fscrapped - meaning those registered
OL,10,Fcan vote for life in General Elections.
OL,12,FThat has seen the number of expats
OL,13,Fable to cast their ballot increase
OL,14,Fdramatically from around one million
OL,15,Fto more than three million.
