OL,3,CConservative rep blames postal vote
OL,4,Cdelays on councils 'ineptitude'
OL,6,FBut while people in the UK will be
OL,7,Fheading to the polls on Thursday 4
OL,8,FJuly, those overseas have to rely on
OL,9,Fpostal ballots or a proxy - where
OL,10,Fsomeone in the UK votes on their
OL,11,Fbehalf.
OL,13,FHowever, many in the Channel Islands
OL,14,Fare still waiting for their ballot to
OL,15,Farrive and with the loss of Jersey's
OL,16,Fmail plane, its postal service says it
OL,17,Fcan only guarantee the vote will get
OL,18,Fback by boat in time to be counted if
OL,19,Fit is sent by Friday 28 June.
