OL,3,CConservative rep blames postal vote
OL,4,Cdelays on councils 'ineptitude'
OL,6,FMr McDowall says the delays are
OL,7,F"extremely disappointing".
OL,9,FHe adds: "Candidly it's down to the
OL,10,Fadministrative ineptitude of the
OL,11,Felectoral returning officers in the
OL,12,Findividual constituencies.
OL,14,F"Someone who lives in Alderney had a
OL,15,Fcall from their electoral returning
OL,16,Fofficer's unit and this poor lady let
OL,17,Fher heart out that there were six of
OL,18,Fthem having to deal with 6,000 postal
OL,19,Fvotes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
