OL,3,CConservative rep blames postal vote
OL,4,Cdelays on councils 'ineptitude'
OL,6,F"It's not working well at all and
OL,7,Fwhichever government is in, I think
OL,8,Fit's one of the technical post-mortem
OL,9,Fissues that has to be dealt with."
OL,11,FClara Slee is a British Citizen living
OL,12,Fin Jersey and has not yet received her
OL,13,Fpostal vote.
OL,15,FShe says: "I received the approval of
OL,16,Fmy postal application two days ago and
OL,17,Fthat was dated 12 June so took about
OL,18,F13 days to arrive but I am still
OL,19,Fwaiting for the ballot.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
